data.text: @RebCS86 Thank you. Getting there! Hopefully it’s got to get better soon x
@ViolasDisguise This happened to me too! Hope you feel ok x
@ViolasDisguise Yes lots of rest is definitely the key. I’m not too bad now thanks. Just mainly very tired
@wanna_disco It comes and goes. Hoping just resting up is helping it pass quicker as I feel worse if I do anything. Hope you’re ok lovely x
@ViolasDisguise Aw Emma, it looks like you got it pretty bad. How are you doing?
@ViolasDisguise Get well soon, we need nice people on twitter to stay alive.
@ViolasDisguise Urg. I tested positive for nearly two weeks with symptoms for about 3-4 days. 2 weeks!! And yet as you say. Allowed to run around if I wanted to. Hope you’re not sick
@ViolasDisguise Fingers crossed it’ll be over soon x
@czarelena It comes and goes. Sometimes I feel ok and then it hits me again. Ugh. So bored of it now. Just glad I’m jabbed up as this could have been so much worse
